/******************************************************
 OFFER ENGINE v5.1 - N8N PRODUCTION RUNTIME
 -----------------------------------------------------
 Supports:
  - Cashflow mandate
  - BRRRR mandate
  - Padsplit mandate
  - Family routing: seller_finance / subto / hybrid
  - Policy-driven ranking
  - Mandate-aware viability
